data.description: This lovely 3-bedroom, 1-bathroom home is ideally located in Niles, just a stone's throw away from the high school and the Apple Festival grounds. Maintained and thoughtfully updated, this property is a charming find.   The fenced-in yard adds a layer of privacy and security.The spacious 24x24 garage is a standout feature, complete with drywall finishing, a convenient small workspace, and a gas heater for year-round comfort. One of the highlights of this home is the brand-new patio, complete with a cozy gazebo. Inside, you'll find newer updates including a furnace, central air unit, and appliances, offering modern convenience and peace of mind.  Don't miss out on the opportunity to call this charming Niles home yours, with its blend of comfort, convenience, and a perfect location close to amenities and community events.
